<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10404781>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Evarcha coreana, holotype male of E. paralbaria. A Prolateral view B Ventral view C Retrolateral view. Abbreviations: dRTA = dorsal retrolateral tibial apophysis, E = embolus, SD = sperm duct, T = tegulum, TA = tegular apophysis, TL = tegular lobe, vRTA = ventral retrolateral tibial apophysis, VTA = ventral tibial apophysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10404781/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10404785>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Evarcha coreana, paratype female of E. paralbaria. A Epigyne, ventral view B Vulva, dorsal view. Abbreviations: CO = copulatory opening, FD = fertilization duct, P = pocket, S = spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10404785/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10404791>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Evarcha coreana, holotype male (A, C, E, G) and allotype female (B, D, F) of E. paralbaria. A, B Habitus, dorsal view C, D Chelicera E–G Original labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10404791/files/figure.png" ;
